widgets.title: Groups Overall & Performance
widgets.desc: The columns in this pivot table are sorted from left to right, with each column sorting within the criteria set by the columns to its left.

This date indicates the hour of last record refresh for ALL data populating this dashboard.

Note: You may encounter report data across dashboards more recent than this timestamp.

content.html: This dynamic dashboard presents timely data pertaining to Branches and associated Groups in the user hierarchy, including the total number of Branches, Groups, Courses associated with each, and engagement—in aggregate, and at the user level—scoped to the level of permission for your account.  Info
